OL,4,CBristol teenager in "unbearable" pain
OL,5,Cdue to eczema
OL,6, A mother has told of her utter
OL,7, desperation at being unable to afford
OL,8, treatment for her son's severe eczema
OL,9, that leaves him "like an open wound".
OL,11,FMiranda Rae from Bristol said it became
OL,12,Fextreme in October and her son Barney,
OL,13,F14, was in constant pain.
OL,15,FShe said a new US drug Dupilumab, that
OL,16,Fcosts #24,000 per year, might help him.
OL,18,FCrowdfunding has raised #7,000 and she
OL,19,Fsaid if they could show the efficacy of
OL,20,Fthe drug, which is unlicensed in the
OL,21,FUK, the NHS might continue treatment.
